---
title: Creamy Potato Salad with Chives & Garlicky Dressing | Serves 2
description: Creamy, zingy, with a hit of onion flavour coming from chives, this potato salad ticks all the boxes! Bonus: we've added the best
garlic aioli to take the flavour factor to another level.
